    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">3–15</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Letter length range</p></div>
  </div>
</div>

<p>DIS- is the single most productive prefix in Scrabble by raw word count. Because it attaches to verbs, nouns, and adjectives alike, you can almost always find an extension if you hold D-I-S on your rack.</p>

